OL,3,CMan behind bars after ramming a
OL,4,Cbulldozer into a village pub
OL,6,FA man is behind bars after ramming a
OL,7,Fbulldozer into a village pub.
OL,9,FDaniel Morgan was handed a 40-month
OL,10,Fprison sentence after causing
OL,11,Fthousands of pounds worth of damage to
OL,12,FThe New Inn in Cefn Rhigos, on
OL,13,FDecember 4, 2025.
OL,15,FMerthyr Tydfil Crown Court heard that
OL,16,Fthe 35-year-old, of Commerce Place,
OL,17,FAberdare, reacted to taunts about his
OL,18,Fmarital breakdown while drunk and
OL,19,Funder the influence of drugs.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
