CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778785872
OL,3,CMan behind bars after ramming a
OL,4,Cbulldozer into a village pub
OL,6,FMorgan then reversed the bulldozer,
OL,7,Fbefore driving off. Her HonourJudge,
OL,8,FCelia Hughes, commended the bravery of
OL,9,FPhillip Morgan and other members of
OL,10,Fthe family, who managed to bring the
OL,11,Fbulldozer to a stop, by smashing the
OL,12,Fcab.
OL,14,FDaniel Morgan had 1.5 times the legal
OL,15,Flimit of alcohol in his blood.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
