OL,3,CMan behind bars after ramming a
OL,4,Cbulldozer into a village pub
OL,6,FIn March, Morgan pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Faggravated vehicle taking, dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving and criminal damage,
OL,9,Frecklessly endangering lives.
OL,11,FToday (May 14) he was sentenced to 12
OL,12,Fmonths in prison concurrent for
OL,13,Faggravated vehicle taking, 12 months
OL,14,Fin prison concurrent for dangerous
OL,15,Fdriving and 40 months in prison for
OL,16,Fcriminal damage, recklessly
OL,17,Fendangering lives. He's been
OL,18,Fdisqualified from driving for 3 years
OL,19,Fand 3 months.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
