OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778785872
OL,3,CMan behind bars after ramming a
OL,4,Cbulldozer into a village pub
OL,6,FThe Judge said she appreciated the
OL,7,Fefforts he has made to remain
OL,8,Fsubstance free.
OL,10,FFollowing sentencing, South Wales
OL,11,FPolice Detective Sergeant Jenna
OL,12,FHerbert, said: "This was a thoughtless
OL,13,Fand targeted attack on a pub.
OL,15,F"Morgan has caused substantive damage
OL,16,Fto both the pub and multiple vehicles,
OL,17,Fit's lucky that no one was seriously
OL,18,Fhurt in this incident."
OL,26,@tD@POU
